OL,7,FLeicestershire Police has referred
OL,8,Fitself to a watchdog over its
OL,9,Finvestigation into alleged attacks by
OL,10,FValdo Calocane in May 2023 ` weeks
OL,11,Fbefore he knifed three people to death
OL,12,Fin Nottingham.
OL,14,FParanoid schizophrenic Calocane, 32,
OL,15,Fafter stabbing 19-year-old students
OL,16,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar and Barnaby
OL,17,FWebber, and school caretaker Ian
OL,18,FCoates, 65, with a dagger in June last
OL,19,Fyear.
OL,21,FHe also ran over city centre.
