OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC) said it was now
OL,9,Fassessing whether any further action
OL,10,Fis required after several incidents
OL,11,Finvolving previous police contact with
OL,12,FCalocane were "brought to their
OL,13,Fattention".
