OL,4,Cprobe into 'assaults' by Nottingham
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FIt emerged during Calocane's
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing last week that in
OL,9,Fearly May 2023 ` around five weeks
OL,10,Fbefore he killed his three victims `
OL,11,FCalocane started working in a
OL,12,Fwarehouse in Kegworth, Leicestershire,
OL,13,Fwhere he was accused of attacking two
OL,14,Femployees.
OL,16,FLeicestershire Police said no one was
OL,17,Fseriously hurt in the factory assault
OL,18,Fand Calocane had reportedly been
OL,19,Fescorted off of the site by security
OL,20,Fbefore police arrived.
