OL,3,CForce refers itself to watchdog over
OL,4,Cprobe into 'assaults' by Nottingham
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FThe IOPC said it requested more
OL,8,Finformation about the attack from
OL,9,FLeicestershire Police after Calocane's
OL,10,Fsentencing last Thursday.
OL,12,FThe watchdog also asked
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police to give more
OL,14,Fdetails about a warrant issued for
OL,15,FCalocane's arrest in 2022 after he
OL,16,Ffailed to appear in court for
OL,17,Fallegedly attacking a police officer.
