OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FIn a statement, the IOPC said:
OL,8,F"Following the sentencing of Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane several incidents involving
OL,10,Fprevious police contact with him have
OL,11,Fbeen brought to our attention which we
OL,12,Fwere unaware of.
OL,14,F"As a result, we asked Nottinghamshire
OL,15,FPolice and Leicestershire Police to
OL,16,Fprovide us with information promptly
OL,17,Fabout those incidents to establish
OL,18,Fwhether there are any matters that
OL,19,Fshould be referred to us.
