OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,F"We have this afternoon received a
OL,8,Freferral from Leicestershire Police
OL,9,Fabout its investigation into assaults
OL,10,FValdo Calocane was alleged to have
OL,11,Fcommitted on May 5 2023, which we are
OL,12,Fassessing to determine what further
OL,13,Faction may be required from us.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
