OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,F"In relation to a warrant being issued
OL,8,Ffor Mr Calocane's arrest in 2022,
OL,9,FNottinghamshire Police provided us
OL,10,Fwith information about that shortly
OL,11,Fafter the tragic events of June 13
OL,12,F2023. We decided it did not meet our
OL,13,Freferral criteria because the contact
OL,14,Fhad not been recent and no conduct
OL,15,Fissues were identified for any
OL,16,Findividual officer.
