OL,7,F"Nottinghamshire Police subsequently
OL,8,Fcarried out an internal review of
OL,9,Fmatters linked to the warrant and we
OL,10,Fhave now also requested details of
OL,11,Fthat learning exercise, in case there
OL,12,Fare any issues that would require our
OL,13,Finvolvement."
